SUMMARY:Girl Scout Robotics Workshop (Brownies\, Juniors\, Cadettes)
DESCRIPTION:Brownie\, Junior\, and Cadette Girl Scouts can fulfill the requirements of all three Robotics Badges right here at the Science Factory! Workshops are held on select Saturdays and require pre-registration. \n$25 per scout. Badges not included. \nClick here to sign up for the March 14\, 2026 Robotics Workshop! \n  \n  \nPlease note our cancellation policy: \n\nCancellations (by the registrant) received less than one week prior to the workshop will be subject to a refund of 1/2 of the total registration cost for that workshop. Cancellations received prior to that shall receive a full refund.\nWorkshops canceled by the Lancaster Science Factory for ANY reason will be refunded fully.
URL:https://lancastersciencefactory.org/event/girl-scout-robotics-workshop-brownies-juniors-cadettes-3/
LOCATION:The Lancaster Science Factory\, 454 New Holland Ave\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
CATEGORIES:Educational Programs
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancastersciencefactory.org/wp-content/uploads/GIRL-SCOUT-ROBOTICS-WORKSHOP-Event-Banner.png
GEO:40.0461822;-76.2963319
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=The Lancaster Science Factory 454 New Holland Ave Lancaster PA 17602 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=454 New Holland Ave:geo:-76.2963319,40.0461822
END:VEVENT
